sellerCard.description: Hi, I am highly experienced Website developer. I have been working with web development since 2018. With more than 5 years of experience as a PHP Laravel developer, I specialize in crafting custom, scalable web applications. From e-commerce platforms to complex enterprise solutions, I deliver results that exceed expectations.

description.content:
Welcome to my PHP Laravel developer or Laravel website development gig. If your Laravel web is suffering from any kind of error or bugs or you want to add new feature to your PHP Laravel website or application or you want to create a new website using PHP or Laravel,


Congratulations !, Then you are on right the gig. I have been working with Laravel since 2018.




Services i am offering:


  • Laravel bug fix

  • Laravel Ecommerce website development
  • Laravel web speed optimization
  • Laravel web SEO
  • Adding new Payment gateways like PayPal, Stripe , bitcoin and many others.

Your task/job/project is not in list ? Don't worry about it i can do every thing in Laravel that is just a list.

questionsAndAnswers.question: How many years of experience you have as php laravel developer?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I have 6 years of experience in website and Laravel Development.

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you provide assistance on a screen share for bug fixing?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: Yes i provided Assistance on a screen share using zoom for your bug fixing

questionsAndAnswers.question: Do you also develop API in Laravel ?
questionsAndAnswers.answer: I can not build new api for you. But i can integrate any api in your web

reviews.comment: very best as always, right now i am working with adeel for some time now and what i really like, besides his perfect work and always available and delivering on time he shares his mind about my project and gives me an opinion, sometimes my mind with how i think things should be could feel as an open end and then feed back is really appreciated, thats what i sometimes miss in working with aseans, i am dutch and here its as blunt and direct it can be, it keeps me having oversight and i like that, thanks adeel

The work was extraordinary. He went well and beyond my expectation for this project he even thought of things that I didn’t think about. I’m so glad he was a part of my project. He fixed all my books and kinks from the previous website, and the turnaround time was outstanding!!!!

I once again had the privilege of working with Adeel, an experienced  developer from Pakistan, and I must say, he exceeded all expectations. Adeel has a knack for seamlessly integrating advanced features like auto-translation in chat applications, making communication across language barriers feel effortless. His implementation was not only functional but intuitive, creating a truly inclusive user experience for global audiences.

What stood out most was his innovative work on blurred group meetings—a feature that ensures privacy and professionalism during virtual meetings. Adeel’s attention to detail in understanding client needs and delivering polished, user-friendly solutions is nothing short of remarkable.

His expertise isn’t just limited to coding; Adeel’s collaborative nature and ability to adapt to feedback make him a joy to work with. He goes above and beyond to ensure satisfaction, delivering projects on time and with finesse.

If you’re looking for a developer who combines technical brilliance with outstanding work ethics, Adeel is the person to hire. His contributions transformed our project into a standout success, and I cannot recommend him enough!

Hire Adeel—you won’t regret it! Joris CS-lite

Professional programer. Best and best working Adeel A. He fixed and edited my website with short time. I recommend.. 
Thank You.
This is the fourth time I’ve used Adeel. He’s the best developer I’ve found on here. Super fast, code is cleanly written and excellent, always responsive.
